Hi @trevor-m, thanks for the fix. At this point, since the PR is already in the merging state internally, it's a bit hard to merge your new changes. I can try to merge them, just FYI. If you have new changes, would you please issue a separate PR after this one is merged? Thanks.

Oh I see, sorry about that. If you are unable to merge any of the changes let me know which ones and I can issue a separate PR later. There won't be any other changes from now on.
